<plot>Thomas Shore needs some time alone. He spends his days making unsolicited sales calls in a crowded call center. His boss berates him and his coworkers smother him. He has planned a relaxing vacation at a beach resort to escape the grind of his daily life. But when he arrives at his destination, he finds these people pursuing him in aggressive and increasingly invasive ways. Featuring a quirky cast including '80s pop sensation Tiffany, The Isolationist is a dark comedy about trying to get away - and failing.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?567044</url></doc>
